(586, 'IP / internet protocol', 'A standard for data communication among devices connected to the Internet.', '', 'n', '', 1, 'core'),
(587, 'IRC / internet relay chat', 'An application that allows users to participate in text based communication with multiple users.', 'Internet Relay Chat (IRC) is a form of real-time Internet chat or synchronous conferencing. It is mainly designed for group communication in discussion forums called channels, but also allows one-to-one communication via private message, as well as chat and data transfers via Direct Client-to-Client.', 'n', '', 1, 'core'),
