(781, 'password', 'A secret combination of typographic characters used to gain admittance or to gain access to information.', 'A password is a secret word or string of characters that is used for authentication, to prove identity or gain access to a resource. The password must be kept secret from those not allowed access.', 'n', '', 1, 'core'),
