(962, 'scan', 'Use an electronic input device to convert information from physical media (such as maps, photographs, and drawings) into a digital format usable by a computer.', 'Scanning is the act of systematically moving a finely focused beam of light or electrons over a surface in order to produce an image of it for analysis or transmission.', 'tv', '', 1, 'core'),
